# List of env var names whose values MUST come from 1Password (op:// refs in .env.local).
#
# bin/start checks each name listed below: if the var is set in the shell, it must
# have an `op://` reference in .env.local. Otherwise bin/start refuses to start.
# Empty lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Uncomment names you want enforced. Add more as needed for your workflow.

# AI keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
# GOOGLE_API_KEY

# Billing / payment
# STRIPE_API_KEY
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY

# Internal services
# BILLING_PRIVATE_KEY
